			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Load up CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;Teleport to -1968; -6; 417&#xD;&#xA;Kill S_LOW_BaneiteOfficer09_0c5259f6-3c86-4e84-b61e-42e9f31691ce&#xD;&#xA;Observe the item being dropped and it hovers near the killed Baneite. The first node is spoken immediately, the second is spoken on the Switch's first turn." />
